description: Flekkefjord Sparebank, a savings bank, provides banking services for retail and corporate markets in lekkefjord, Egersund, Farsund, Hægebostad, Kvinesdal, Lindesnes, Lund, Lyngdal, and SirdalogSokndal. It offers mortgage, car, boat, moving mortgage, mortgages for young people, cottage, and construction loans; bank, Boligsparing for ungdom, mutual fund, Borea, stock trading, and retirement savings; and business loans/credit and financing, guarantees, and leasing facilities. The company also provides life and personal, house and contents, vehicle, travel and leisure, property, and liability insurance products; and mobile and online banking, cards, accounts, bankID, watch and mobile payment, foreign payments, contract giro and eInvoice, telebank, and Vips services, as well as pension services. Flekkefjord Sparebank was founded in 1837 and is headquartered in Flekkefjord, Norway.
